						<div class="postbody">Unfortunately I don't have any ideas... I'd probably have to look at some code, and I'm not sure if you're willing to post code since this is for a compo... looking at your NMI/VBlank handler would help, for example.
<br />
<br /><div class="quotetitle">strat wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I'll try burning 512 cycles after the DMA write (Just checked the wiki)</div>
<br />You don't have to burn anything. When you request a sprite DMA the CPU stays busy for that long while doing the transfer, there's nothing you're supposed to do about that.</div>

