					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">It looks like you're not setting the the sprite address, $2003.  Since the main loop seems to be executing from the NMI while disabling/enabling it, it seems likely that the sprite address could somehow be in an unexpected state (depending on the time taken for all execution and branches etc.).  Also would be bad if it's happens to be enabled during a partial vblank (the hardware interrupt is level-sensitive, triggered by state rather than changes).
<br />
<br />And yeah as said, LDA $2000 I guess would be equivalent to doing LDA #$20.</div>

